==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reassert
<hw>Re`as*sert"</hw> <pr>(r⟦emac⟧`⟦acr⟧s*s⟦etil⟧rt")</pr>, <pos>v.
t.</pos> <def>To assert again or anew; to maintain after an omission to
do so.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Let us hope . . . we may have a body of authors who will
<qex>reassert</qex> our claim to respectability in literature.</q>
<rj><qau>Walsh.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reassertion</ent>⟦br⟧
